('F063', 'INC', 'Click Dk', 'DK', 'Classics', 'f063-large.jpg', 45, 36, 65, 50, 1, 11, '150m/164y', '70% Acrylic, 30% Wool', 'Click Dk is a classic yarn with 30% wool that comes in modern fashion shades.Click Dk''s eye-catching colours make dramatic looking fashion knits to wear in the city for every day style. Click Dk''s wool and acrylic blend is easy care and easy wear.', NULL),
