('F045', 'INC', 'Click Chunky with Wool', 'Chunky', 'Classics', 'f045-large.jpg', 47, 36, 68, 50, 1, 12, '75m/82y', '70% Acrylic, 30% Wool', 'Click is rapidly becoming a favourite with knitters and comes in a range of soft colours and marls that work well for all the family. If you want to knit your first Chunky yarn, Click is perfect for you and knits up quickly too. Click Chunky''s wool and acrylic blend will keep its quality through repeated machine washing.', NULL),
